│ than fixed-width vectors, the assertion should allow this disagreement when │
│ comparing scalar vs scalable VFs.\n\n5. Conclusion: The fix modifies the    │
│ assertion to permit disagreement between scalar and scalable vectorization  │
│ factors, recognizing that these represent fundamentally different           │
│ vectorization approaches that may legitimately lead to different optimal    │
│ choices between the legacy and VPlan cost models."})                        │
